Subject: Password Reset
Description:
Hi, I cannot login to my EPP server. For some reason my password is no longer being accepted and I cannot reset my password. 

How can I reset my password so I can login to my EPP server? The server is hosted by CoSoSys
What_We_Know__c: The customer could not log in the EPP Server with their password.
Next_Steps__c:
The password was reset to the default password.
Waiting for the customer to confirm if the log in works and if the ticket can be closed.
